      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BIZZIE LIZZIE (1) registered a strong performance in Victoria last time when she raced parked but battled on well for a 2.3m second at Hamilton. Has switched to the Grant Jones yard since and won a trial for that stable. Proven at this distance and is likely to get the favours from this nice draw so can make an immediate impact. SAVOY BALLROOM (4) has some good performances at this circuit under her belt including a win from a wide barrier over this distance last month. Can measure up in this line up. MY ULTIMATE FRANCO NZ (2) draws much better than last start and had some decent form in Queensland prior including a second two back at Albion Park so is worth another chance. BAM BAM BROOK (7) draws wide but should be ready to peak fourth up after showing improvement in finishing second at Canberra last time out.",
